name: UMonoWaveTableSynthPreset
doc: UStruct Mono Wave Table Synth Preset

LockKeyframesToGrid: How many evenly-spaced keyframes to use when LockKeyframesToGrid is true
WaveTableResolution: How many samples will be taken of the curve from time = [0.0, 1.0]
bLockKeyframesToGridBool: Lock wavetables to evenly spaced keyframes that can be edited vertically only (will re-sample)
bNormalizeWaveTables: Normalize the WaveTable data? False will allow clipping, True will normalize the tables when sent to the synth for rendering
